	<div style="text-align:right;">
		MELLO, Luiz Guilherme Natalio de<sup>1</sup>; SOUZA, Maristela Denise Marques de<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
